snippet.title: Space Travellers - Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Game page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2345340/Space_Travellers/

Space Travellers is a unique open-world sandbox space simulator. The player has complete freedom of decision and movement. You can travel to familiar places in the Solar System and adjacent systems, or explore over 6000 unexplored distant worlds.
